Package: gridwell
Title: Fast Multi-Format Table Rendering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Richard", "Iannone", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "riannone@me.com")
Description: Renders table IR (Intermediate Representation) to many output
    formats including HTML, LaTeX, Typst, RTF, SVG, ANSI, Pandoc, Quarto,
    DOCX, XLSX, and PPTX. Powered by a Rust backend via extendr.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    jsonlite
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/rextendr/version: 0.5.0
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
